{"tid":911639,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【黑客攻擊】恒生大學被嚴重入侵 全校師生Google Drive癱瘓","createTime":"2018-11-22T05:11:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T08:34:49.000Z","uid":150014,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2d814a624ac024154d52256d306f75a4ad6087d1","tid":911639,"uid":150014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:11:44.000Z","msg":"【黑客攻擊】恒生大學被嚴重入侵 全校師生Google Drive癱瘓<br />\n38分鐘前<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港恒生大學所有師生的Gmail電郵帳戶昨晚突遭關閉，校方向學生交代的通告指出，Google稱懷疑校方的電郵戶口遭黑客入侵，連續寄出垃圾電郵，因而自動停止運作，需經過一定程序才能重新啟動。<br />\n<br />\n香港恒生大學的Gmail電郵帳戶由昨夜約7時半遭關閉，Google Drive功能亦受影響，導致同學文件、功課均不能取存。校方對學生指，由於不少老師及同學均會用Google Drive下載文件，擔心會嚴重影響上課及工作，呼籲各位老師同學互相幫忙，日後不應過度依賴Google。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n直至今早11時30分，恒大所有Google帳戶才回復正常運作。本報正向恒大查詢事件，截稿前尚未回覆。<br />\n<br />\n香港恒生大學現有約有5,000名全日制學生及約200名全職教師。上月底，政府通過恒生管理學院正名為大學，成為第二間私立大學，並剛於11月8日舉行正名啟動禮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181122/58943580\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181122%2F58943580&d=dfeeB01biWcpSatpjJUPM6NGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=e945ad52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181122%2F58943580&h=f7a5f359\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181122/58943580</a>"},{"pid":"1e9ebe313c8167e47bb97946a0fdb374e1e901d6","tid":911639,"uid":12021,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:12:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81dafebdb54a78851b0e501d54effb9878a3fd28","tid":911639,"uid":30377,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e9ebe313c8167e47bb97946a0fdb374e1e901d6","tid":911639,"uid":12021,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:12:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:14:02.000Z","msg":"唔係通常有自己email嫁咩"},{"pid":"9abe8efdced858d221909